      <title>大选后美国房屋建筑商信心达到七个月高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/us-homebuilder-sentiment-reaches-seven-month-high-after-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于销售预期上升且市场对特朗普政府将减轻监管负担感到乐观，美国房屋建筑商的信心在 11 月份升至七个月高位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/us-homebuilder-sentiment-reaches-seven-month-high-after-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>魁北克省 CDPQ 押注量化策略并渴望做更多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/quebec-s-cdpq-bets-on-quant-strategies-and-is-eager-to-do-more</link>
      <description><![CDATA[魁北克公共养老基金经理在不到四年的时间内已将其量化股票团队的资产扩大到 140 多亿美元，而该基金的一位高管对实现更大目标充满信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/quebec-s-cdpq-bets-on-quant-strategies-and-is-eager-to-do-more</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 14:53:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>凯尔·巴斯谈特朗普的财政部选择和中国的刺激计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-18/bass-on-trump-s-treasury-pick-china-s-stimulus-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[海曼资本管理公司 (Hayman Capital Management) 创始人凯尔·巴斯 (Kyle Bass) 表示，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 应该任命斯科特·贝森 (Scott Bessent) 为财政部长。他还表示，中国经济正在“走下坡路”。他说刺激计划毫无成效。巴斯正在接受“彭博监视”节目采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-18/bass-on-trump-s-treasury-pick-china-s-stimulus-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 14:35:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲银行首席执行官称希腊银行拥有“过剩资本”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-18/banks-in-greece-have-excess-capital-eurobank-ceo-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲银行 Ergasias 服务与控股公司首席执行官 Fokion Karavias 周一在彭博社组织的小组讨论会上表示，希腊银行拥有“过剩资本”，他们将利用这些资本来融资增长、向投资者支付部分回报并寻求收购。Karavias 还引用了近年来在保加利亚和塞浦路斯的收购，证明希腊银行正在成为积极的整合者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-18/banks-in-greece-have-excess-capital-eurobank-ceo-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 14:30:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ESMA 建议欧盟于 2027 年 10 月效仿美国实施 T+1 制度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/esma-recommends-eu-follows-us-move-to-t-1-in-october-2027</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟市场监管机构建议欧盟在 2027 年底将证券交易结算时间从两天缩短至一天，此举将使该地区重新与美国同步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/esma-recommends-eu-follows-us-move-to-t-1-in-october-2027</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 13:45:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在激进主义者的压力下，CVS 将 Glenview 的 Robbins 纳入董事会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/cvs-appoints-glenview-s-robbins-to-board-under-activist-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[CVS Health Corp. 任命 Glenview Capital Management 创始人 Larry Robbins 加入其董事会，这是与一直在向该公司施压要求变革的激进公司达成的协议的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/cvs-appoints-glenview-s-robbins-to-board-under-activist-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 12:07:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>防御力弱刺激资金外流，对冲基金抛售土耳其里拉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/lira-losses-deepen-as-funds-react-to-state-banks-lifting-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，由于国有银行未积极捍卫汇率，且交易员平掉部分套利交易，土耳其里拉周一贬值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/lira-losses-deepen-as-funds-react-to-state-banks-lifting-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 11:51:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>零售商的假日展望将考验美国消费者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/earnings-season-faces-major-test-retailers-holiday-outlooks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周的抛售就发生在美国企业普遍成功的财报季之后，投资者正准备迎接最后一个考验：未来几天将公布的一系列零售业领头羊的零售业报告，以了解消费者的消费状况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/earnings-season-faces-major-test-retailers-holiday-outlooks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 10:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国 10 年期国债收益率接近 4.5%，股市陷入困境：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/asian-stocks-eye-soft-start-as-fed-doubts-simmer-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国国债收益率进一步下滑，股市难以找到方向，10 年期国债收益率接近 4.5% 大关，交易员密切关注当选总统唐纳德·特朗普政府的新闻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/asian-stocks-eye-soft-start-as-fed-doubts-simmer-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 22:32:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普团队正寻求放宽美国自动驾驶汽车规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/trump-team-said-to-want-to-ease-us-rules-for-self-driving-cars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的过渡团队成员告诉顾问，他们计划将自动驾驶汽车的联邦框架作为交通部的优先事项之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/trump-team-said-to-want-to-ease-us-rules-for-self-driving-cars</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 20:43:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
